    <string name="changelog_title">What\'s New</string>
    <string name="changelog_content">\u2022 <b>Bluetooth Battery Glyph</b>: View connected device battery level on the Glyph bar for 4s when flipped.\n\n\u2022 <b>9-Zone Visualization</b>: Volume and Battery animations now use the full progress strip and the DOT LED (9 zones).\n\n\u2022 <b>Essential Light Fixes</b>: Lights now activate immediately after animations and correctly across lock/unlock cycles.\n\n\u2022 <b>UI Improvements</b>: Fixed text and toggle clipping in Battery settings.\n\n\u2022 <b>Improved Media Progress</b>: Real-time music and download progress is now more reliable and respects flipped-only settings (8-zone LINE only).\n\n\u2022 <b>Shake to Glyph Optimization</b>: Better sensitivity control and screen-on/off logic.\n\n\u2022 <b>Rebranded to NGlyph</b>: New look and improved native hardware integration.</string>
